Ebony Salmon is one of the most exciting ballers in the Barclays WSL. With razor-sharp feet and sprint speed that puts her among the fastest players in the game, she’s got all the attributes needed to be a five-star five-a-side player. In the latest episode of ‘Barclays WSL Behind the Baller Series 3’, she tells us why small-sided football still gives her a rush unlike anything else.⁣
⁣
Take to the pitch with your ultimate Aston Villa 5-a-side team in Rush now.
